  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Light, medium, heavy:</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">they can be worn without problems by those with the necessary proficiency. If worn without competency, characters suffer from disadvantage to hit rolls, ability checks and saving throws and are unable to cast spells.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Aristocratic:</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">weapons and armor with this property are indicative of a certain position in society or at least wealth. Wearing them implies a high social status, for better or for worse.</span> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /></span></p>",
